One of our favourite smoothies! 
 Recipe – 1 Glass:

1 cup fresh watermelon, seedless
1/2 cup cold water
1/2 lime, squeezed
1 tsp maple syrup
pinch of salt

Blend all ingredients until smooth. Feel free to add ice or free the watermelon beforehand. Enjoy!
